---
import ShowcaseLayout from '../../../layouts/ShowcaseLayout.astro';
---
<ShowcaseLayout
  title="About Lumiere Salon & Spa — Our Story"
  description="Learn about Lumiere Salon & Spa — founded in 2014 by Isabelle Laurent, a sanctuary for beauty, wellness, and self-care in the heart of the city."
  backColor="#E8D5C4"
  backBg="rgba(28, 20, 16, 0.85)"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bodoni+Moda:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=Raleway:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </Fragment>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --espresso: #1C1410; --espresso-soft: #251A14;
      --espresso-card: #2A1F18;
      --blush: #E8D5C4; --blush-dim: rgba(232,213,196,0.6);
      --blush-muted: rgba(232,213,196,0.3);
      --champagne: #C9A96E; --champagne-light: #DFC08A;
      --champagne-dim: rgba(201,169,110,0.15);
      --border: rgba(232,213,196,0.1); --border-gold: rgba(201,169,110,0.25);
      --ff-display: 'Bodoni Moda', Georgia, serif;
      --ff-body: 'Raleway', system-ui, sans-serif;
      --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
    }
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{background:var(--espresso);color:var(--blush);font-family:var(--ff-body);overflow-x:hidden}
    a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
    ul{list-style:none}
    .back-btn{background:rgba(28,20,16,0.85);color:var(--blush);border:1px solid var(--border)}

    /* NAV */
    .nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;transition:background .4s,border-color .4s;border-bottom:1px solid transparent}
    .nav.scrolled{background:rgba(28,20,16,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);border-bottom-color:var(--border)}
    .nav__inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:80px}
    .nav__logo{font-family:var(--ff-display);font-size:1.4rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--blush);letter-spacing:0.02em}
    .nav__logo span{color:var(--champagne)}
    .nav__links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2.5rem}
    .nav__link{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blush-muted);transition:color .2s;position:relative}
    .nav__link::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-3px;left:0;width:0;height:1px;background:var(--champagne);transition:width .3s ease}
    .nav__link:hover,.nav__link:focus-visible{color:var(--blush);outline:none}
    .nav__link:hover::after,.nav__link:focus-visible::after{width:100%}
    .nav__book{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--espresso);background:var(--champagne);padding:.55rem 1.3rem;transition:background .2s,transform .2s}
    .nav__book:hover,.nav__book:focus-visible{background:var(--champagne-light);transform:translateY(-1px);outline:none;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px var(--espresso), 0 0 0 4px var(--champagne)}

    /* ABOUT HERO */
    .about-hero{padding:10rem 2rem 5rem;background:var(--espresso);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .about-hero__ornament{position:absolute;pointer-events:none;border-radius:50%}
    .about-hero__ornament--1{top:-60px;right:-100px;width:400px;height:400px;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1)}
    .about-hero__ornament--2{bottom:-80px;left:-60px;width:300px;height:300px;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.06)}
    .about-hero__inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4rem;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:1}
    .about-hero__text{max-width:520px}
    .about-hero__tag{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--champagne);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
    .about-hero__tag::before,.about-hero__tag::after{content:'';display:inline-block;width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--champagne);opacity:.5}
    .about-hero__tag::before{display:none}
    .about-hero__title{font-family:var(--ff-display);font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.8rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.1;color:var(--blush);margin-bottom:1.5rem}
    .about-hero__title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--champagne)}
    .about-hero__lead{font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--blush-dim);line-height:1.85;font-weight:300;font-style:italic}
    .about-hero__photo-wrap{position:relative}
    .about-hero__photo{width:100%;aspect-ratio:3/4;object-fit:cover;display:block;filter:brightness(0.95) contrast(1.05)}
    .about-hero__photo-border{position:absolute;top:12px;left:12px;right:-12px;bottom:-12px;border:1px solid var(--border-gold);pointer-events:none}

    /* STORY */
    .story-section{padding:6rem 2rem;background:var(--espresso-soft)}
    .story-inner{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}
    .story-tag{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--champagne);margin-bottom:1.2rem;text-align:center}
    .story-title{font-family:var(--ff-display);font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;color:var(--blush);margin-bottom:2rem;text-align:center}
    .story-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--champagne)}
    .story-text{font-size:1rem;color:var(--blush-dim);line-height:1.85;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
    .story-text:last-child{margin-bottom:0}

    /* VALUES */
    .values-section{padding:6rem 2rem;background:var(--espresso)}
    .values-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
    .values-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);margin-top:3rem}
    .value-item{padding:2.5rem;background:var(--espresso);border-right:1.5px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1.5px solid var(--border);transition:background .3s}
    .value-item:hover{background:var(--espresso-card)}
    .value-item:nth-child(3n){border-right:none}
    .value-item:nth-last-child(-n+3){border-bottom:none}
    .value-item__name{font-family:var(--ff-display);font-size:1.4rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--blush);margin-bottom:.6rem}
    .value-item__desc{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--blush-muted);line-height:1.75;font-weight:300}

    /* CTA */
    .about-cta{padding:6rem 2rem;background:var(--espresso-soft);text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
    .about-cta::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:500px;height:500px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(201,169,110,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
    .about-cta__inner{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto}
    .about-cta__title{font-family:var(--ff-display);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem);font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;color:var(--blush);margin-bottom:1rem}
    .about-cta__title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--champagne)}
    .about-cta__sub{font-size:1rem;color:var(--blush-dim);line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:2.5rem}
    .btn-primary{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;background:var(--champagne);color:var(--espresso);padding:.9rem 2.2rem;font-family:var(--ff-body);font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:background .25s ease,transform .25s ease,box-shadow .25s ease}
    .btn-primary:hover,.btn-primary:focus-visible{background:var(--champagne-light);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(201,169,110,0.3);outline:none}

    .db-credit{text-align:center;padding:2rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border);font-size:.76rem;color:var(--blush-muted)}
    .db-credit a{color:var(--champagne);font-weight:600}

    @media(max-width:768px){
      .about-hero__inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2.5rem}
      .about-hero__photo-wrap{max-width:400px;margin:0 auto}
      .values-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .value-item{border-right:none}
      .value-item:nth-child(3n){border-right:none}
    }
  </style>

  <nav class="nav scrolled" id="nav">
    <div class="nav__inner">
      <a href="/showcase/salon" class="nav__logo"><span>Lumi</span>ere</a>
      <ul class="nav__links">
        <li><a href="/showcase/salon#services" class="nav__link">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="/showcase/salon#gallery" class="nav__link">Gallery</a></li>
        <li><a href="/showcase/salon/about" class="nav__link">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/showcase/salon#book" class="nav__link">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="/showcase/salon#book" class="nav__book">Book Now</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero__ornament about-hero__ornament--1"></div>
    <div class="about-hero__ornament about-hero__ornament--2"></div>
    <div class="about-hero__inner">
      <div class="about-hero__text reveal">
        <div class="about-hero__tag">Our Story</div>
        <h1 class="about-hero__title">Beauty is a<br/>form of <em>care.</em></h1>
        <p class="about-hero__lead">Founded in 2014 by Isabelle Laurent, Lumiere Salon & Spa was born from a simple belief: that everyone deserves a space where they can slow down, feel seen, and leave feeling like the best version of themselves.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero__photo-wrap reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580618672591-eb180b1a973f?w=600&h=800&fit=crop&crop=top&auto=format"
          alt="Isabelle Laurent, founder of Lumiere Salon & Spa"
          class="about-hero__photo"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <div class="about-hero__photo-border"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-inner reveal">
      <div class="story-tag">The Beginning</div>
      <h2 class="story-title">From a single chair<br/>to a <em>sanctuary.</em></h2>
      <p class="story-text">Isabelle spent over a decade working in salons across the country before returning to her hometown with a vision. She wanted to create something different — not just a place to get your hair done, but a place where the experience itself was the point.</p>
      <p class="story-text">Lumiere opened its doors in a small storefront on Willow Lane with two styling chairs, a kettle for tea, and an unwavering commitment to craft. Word spread quickly. Clients came for the precision cuts and stayed for the feeling of being genuinely cared for.</p>
      <p class="story-text">Today, the salon has grown into a full-service studio with a team of eight talented stylists and wellness practitioners. The tea kettle is still there — and so is the philosophy. Every appointment begins with a conversation, because beauty that lasts starts with listening.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="values-inner">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center">
        <div class="story-tag">What We Believe</div>
        <h2 class="story-title">Guided by <em>intention.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-item reveal">
          <div class="value-item__name">Craft Over Speed</div>
          <p class="value-item__desc">We never rush a service. Every cut, color, and treatment is given the time and attention it deserves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="value-item__name">Clean Beauty</div>
          <p class="value-item__desc">We use only cruelty-free, sustainably sourced products that are as kind to the earth as they are to your skin and hair.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="value-item__name">Inclusive Space</div>
          <p class="value-item__desc">Lumiere is for everyone. We celebrate all textures, styles, and identities — no exceptions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="about-cta__inner reveal">
      <h2 class="about-cta__title">Ready to<br/><em>experience it?</em></h2>
      <p class="about-cta__sub">Book your first visit and see why our clients never want to leave.</p>
      <a href="/showcase/salon#book" class="btn-primary">Book an Appointment</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    const nav = document.getElementById('nav');
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      nav.classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 40);
    }, { passive: true });
  </script>
</ShowcaseLayout>
